{"url":"https://www.pref.aichi.jp/site/kyoinsaiyou/2026setumeikai.html","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"ja\">\r\n<head>\r\n\r\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-NBYG67KKXX\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-NBYG67KKXX');\n</script>\r\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"教員採用\">\r\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"\">\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n<title>令和9年度(2027年度)採用愛知県公立学校教員採用選考試験説明会について - 愛知県公立学校教員採用選考試験について - 愛知県</title>\r\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/vnd.microsoft.icon\">\n<link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/vnd.microsoft.icon\">\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\" href=\"/ssi/css/print.css\">\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/escapeurl.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/jquery.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/jquery-migrate.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/common.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/s-google.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/search-trend.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/search-open-page-id.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/last-page-parts-load-1.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/ssi/js/footstep.js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/ssi/css/footstep.css\">\n<meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\">\r\n<style  media=\"all\">\r\n@import url(\"/ssi/css/site.css\");\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://fair-navi.com/loader/loader.js\" data-fairnavi=\"ihr2baf7\"></script>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"fb-root\"></div>\r\n<script async defer crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/ja_JP/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v23.0\"></script>\r\n<!-- レコメンドここから -->\r\n<script src=\"/